\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e44bda09202fc6cdb31414d316688e61c98f4e","tid":2017242,"uid":319247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"其實好似個鬼佬咁將9聲縮做6聲（唔要尾個3個）<br />\n可能會容易dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388a2a30b5bdd34ecaa7addd7a3ead3784bae3b1","tid":2017242,"uid":162535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c303c3ba09057890c6fc65d42eb785d87ffa952a","tid":2017242,"uid":175346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16519191ccc885f3172b9d163b75504643684909","tid":2017242,"uid":162535,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"世界仔黎，想搵飯食，似偽中立<br />\n佢對香港無乜認識架，最開頭語言天才個朵上咗下日本電視，支那紅咗排跟住紅唔起<br />\n奶共失敗之後拍廣東話片見個views進步咗就繼續拍廣東話片咁解<br />\n<br />\n其實佢views低只係因為d片真係悶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"廣東話所謂的「難學」係因為無一個比較標準的課程同太多教材去教廣東話，加粵語+香港文化比中國騎劫咗(外國眼中的中國風好多係香港風黎)<br />\n<br />\n「廣東話難學」呢個feel其實係同日本人講日文難學類似，但仍然會有好多人肯去學日文<br />\n<br />\n兩者個分別其實就係文化推廣程度不同+有無系統教學<br />\n<br />\n同埋立場呢d野，我都希望佢見到講廣東話有市場會放棄中國，但個人黎講暫時都係有保留，畢竟佢本身第一target係中國人"},{"pid":"425c7aee66ea78a155cffae3dcea5b2e76d1cecc","tid":2017242,"uid":175346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b3ce33fbacaef9bf7b5398f21693dc3acdc865","tid":2017242,"uid":175346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33e6241aa65103fa66b23db018a973f85af45b3f","tid":2017242,"uid":91605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b02e8babe88c7a7eefc6c1625b95fc78052971a","tid":2017242,"uid":93450,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"鬼佬學就緊係難 唔同語系<br />\n但平心粵語grammar簡單到離譜<br />\n冇tense冇gender冇case<br />\n係難掌握在聲調同語尾助詞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"對外國人嚟講tense先係易，啲聲調語尾冇規則先係最難"},{"pid":"50326408608822be2d4d87bf933d993d22f0e8ee","tid":2017242,"uid":314731,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d335dfdf021ef976e0d72a0c898246dbff89ab7","tid":2017242,"uid":100016,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0b702ba89ae37ed2b3ef8347c382a8e10f7c9d89","tid":2017242,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f9283c74bd71ad99f87bd22c4cbf6cb150e7d6a","tid":2017242,"uid":100016,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"奶共狗黎，unsub左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"how?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"自己睇下佢其他片啦，周圍叫人同中國講生日快樂又剩，條友依家根本係想打中國市場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"如果唔係都唔會簡體字啦<br />\n初初都有睇<br />\n之後都un左"},{"pid":"60b8e6893881b483de644558c719baf1551a6cc7","tid":2017242,"uid":314731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16519191ccc885f3172b9d163b75504643684909","tid":2017242,"uid":162535,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"世界仔黎，想搵飯食，似偽中立<br />\n佢對香港無乜認識架，最開頭語言天才個朵上咗下日本電視，支那紅咗排跟住紅唔起<br />\n奶共失敗之後拍廣東話片見個views進步咗就繼續拍廣東話片咁解<br />\n<br />\n其實佢views低只係因為d片真係悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"同埋真係無咩剪接過<br />\n拍完cut 最頭同最尾就放上去"},{"pid":"618876f0d8e750a271bee8f45b4e9539f6349aba","tid":2017242,"uid":141033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"當你淨係識普通話都可以喺香港生活到，除非個外國人真係好鍾意香港文化，如果係想學門實用嘅語言點會揀廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同難唔難無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f7364a3abb9d516d91d58ef2d583613bdf502a","tid":2017242,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e17ca5d2aae543797111b745ded069bce4b8e933","tid":2017242,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84513ba478dfdaafdd576c1e0365072a372a47fb","tid":2017242,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"個加拿大鬼佬都講得好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"人地識20種語言 香港真係冇乜依d天才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"其實大家睇外國啲polyglot channel，話就話「識」廿種語言，但每隻語言喺proficiency上一定有所不同<br />\n通常都係有幾隻最流利最常用，然後其他做到普通日常對話，加幾隻學緊咁<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔使太睇低自己，淨係有學日/韓文，已經粵普英日/韓4隻落袋，亦都有識10+隻話嘅香港人拍片，不過唔係普通YouTuber嗰種姐<br />\n而且差異越細、同一族嘅語言，通常越學越快上手"},{"pid":"3c31929027e563328ecae42930b6262884b9297a","tid":2017242,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"學識講好容易囉明明<br />\n是但放d次序其實都明<br />\n難係難在要記同睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99da257559f8083f20f89c03b1f2cb15eecb06bf","tid":2017242,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e17ca5d2aae543797111b745ded069bce4b8e933","tid":2017242,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84513ba478dfdaafdd576c1e0365072a372a47fb","tid":2017242,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"個加拿大鬼佬都講得好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"人地識20種語言 香港真係冇乜依d天才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"你試下去入下香港啲語言group睇下啲人，都好撚癲先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF56CXGSXVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUF56CXGSXVc&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=83cb0205\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF56CXGSXVc</a>"},{"pid":"845d500969595f5654a75b56b3619c7d0ae1e612","tid":2017242,"uid":66994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27f7364a3abb9d516d91d58ef2d583613bdf502a","tid":2017242,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e17ca5d2aae543797111b745ded069bce4b8e933","tid":2017242,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84513ba478dfdaafdd576c1e0365072a372a47fb","tid":2017242,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"個加拿大鬼佬都講得好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"人地識20種語言 香港真係冇乜依d天才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"其實大家睇外國啲polyglot channel，話就話「識」廿種語言，但每隻語言喺proficiency上一定有所不同<br />\n通常都係有幾隻最流利最常用，然後其他做到普通日常對話，加幾隻學緊咁<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔使太睇低自己，淨係有學日/韓文，已經粵普英日/韓4隻落袋，亦都有識10+隻話嘅香港人拍片，不過唔係普通YouTuber嗰種姐<br />\n而且差異越細、同一族嘅語言，通常越學越快上手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"其實polyglot香港都有，只不過唔出名，前登都有個Lingo巴"},{"pid":"b3f9273d5f881d388a3157d9c992c97bea22c4eb","tid":2017242,"uid":242602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"1，大多數鬼佬學中文都係想同大陸做生意，冇乜原因要學廣東話<br />\n<br />\n2，台灣都係普通話（字眼有啲唔同但係總括黎講都係差唔多發音）<br />\n<br />\n3，香港嘅知識水平比較高，相對大陸黎講講英文冇問題，基本上差唔多所有香港公司嘅內部email都係英文<br />\n<br />\n3.5，承上，除咗香港之外，根本冇值得做生意嘅城市用廣東話做母語<br />\n<br />\n4，英文同日文某程度上無音調呢樣嘢，支那話四個音調對佢哋黎講已經好難，何況廣東話九個音，叫佢哋分「雖，水，碎，誰，緒，睡」真係死比你睇"},{"pid":"d0980c386fec9e4643e4b8e2036703aa3f08efe2","tid":2017242,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"首先，真係冇乜香港人話廣東話好難。第二，其他人學唔學廣東話根本就唔會理香港人點講，上reddit r/Cantonese就知好多人有學。教材書都有幾本 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.linguajunkie.com/cantonese/cantonese-textbooks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linguajunkie.com%2Fcantonese%2Fcantonese-textbooks&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=eeec7dbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linguajunkie.com/cantonese/cantonese-textbooks</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打特登開咗howtostudycantonese出教材"},{"pid":"45184bad6bd72a637c5c6fdb972bd3d3a81ead08","tid":2017242,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f9273d5f881d388a3157d9c992c97bea22c4eb","tid":2017242,"uid":242602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"1，大多數鬼佬學中文都係想同大陸做生意，冇乜原因要學廣東話<br />\n<br />\n2，台灣都係普通話（字眼有啲唔同但係總括黎講都係差唔多發音）<br />\n<br />\n3，香港嘅知識水平比較高，相對大陸黎講講英文冇問題，基本上差唔多所有香港公司嘅內部email都係英文<br />\n<br />\n3.5，承上，除咗香港之外，根本冇值得做生意嘅城市用廣東話做母語<br />\n<br />\n4，英文同日文某程度上無音調呢樣嘢，支那話四個音調對佢哋黎講已經好難，何況廣東話九個音，叫佢哋分「雖，水，碎，誰，緒，睡」真係死比你睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"其實廣東話得六個音調<br />\n所謂789聲，只係傳統將同136聲同調嘅ptk尾入聲字分開處理<br />\n但呢種做法喺出現變調嘅情況下就描述唔到實際聲調，例如消防局個局字咁<br />\n好似粵拼咁淨係用123456好過"},{"pid":"562fad935f5735f506baa11e2d723917474ff25a","tid":2017242,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99da257559f8083f20f89c03b1f2cb15eecb06bf","tid":2017242,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e17ca5d2aae543797111b745ded069bce4b8e933","tid":2017242,"uid":200529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84513ba478dfdaafdd576c1e0365072a372a47fb","tid":2017242,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"個加拿大鬼佬都講得好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"人地識20種語言 香港真係冇乜依d天才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"你試下去入下香港啲語言group睇下啲人，都好撚癲先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF56CXGSXVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUF56CXGSXVc&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=83cb0205\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UF56CXGSXVc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"呢條友好明題日文之外既語言，用google translate完，貼張紙係前面齋讀， 佢d韓文好多音都發錯晒，仲話學左4年，笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4c9b3a8d853cb